  ${
    $d w x y A $.
    subbas2.1 $e |- B =
           { x | E. y ( y (_ A /\ y e. Fin /\ x = |^| y ) } $.
    $( The collection of finite intersections of any set (subbasis) ` A ` is
       a basis for a topology on ` U. A ` .  Justifies the definition of
       subbasis in [Munkres] p. 82 (after using ~ unitg ). $)
